Sprott Precious Metals
Expertise and track record of innovation

Sprott is a globally recognized leader in precious metals investing. Over the years, we’ve designed and developed innovative investment products for investors – from equity and bullion mutual funds, to exchange-traded bullion and equity solutions – that address very specific needs within their portfolios.


